name: MYZEAL IT Solutions
overview:
MYZEAL IT Solutions is one of the pioneers in providing unique, quality-based end-to-end IT solutions to customers based across the globe.

Since inception, we have been offering software development services such as Application Management, Product Engineering, Mobile Engineering and Valued Added Services to help clients transform their business with minimal risk and disruption. With our passionate IT Solutions, we provide organizations greater flexibility, higher efficiency and lower costs.

Our enhanced project collaboration tools and well-codified business process assure consistent, well planned scalable, measurable and reliable delivery model to clients based at any locations of the world. With our client-friendly, pragmatic, never-heard-before engagement models, you can turn your ideas into reality.

Specialties Offshore Website Development, Software Development, Application Management, Product Development, Mobile Applications, Value added services, Independent Testing, Incubation Services for Startups, Content Management Services

Headquarters Plot #83, NSEZ Phase II Noida, Noida 201305 India

Website http://www.myzealit.com

Industry Computer Software
